{"tid":39213,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"大幅度修改程式碼 新增機制加強穩定 Linux Kernel 4.9 歷來最大更新版","createTime":"2016-12-14T12:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T02:17:51.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc482a182ff5644cfda03c90d128d87ca91bf2f4","tid":39213,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:21:01.000Z","msg":"大幅度修改程式碼 新增機制加強穩定<br />\nLinux Kernel 4.9 歷來最大更新版<img src=\"https://ka-sir.xyz/p/HKG_icon/BrainMonster/10.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fka-sir.xyz%2Fp%2FHKG_icon%2FBrainMonster%2F10.gif&h=606ff80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkepc.com/14709/大幅度修改程式碼_新增機制加強穩定__Linux_Kernel_4.9_歷來最大更新版\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F14709%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E5%BA%A6%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F%E7%A2%BC_%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E7%A9%A9%E5%AE%9A__Linux_Kernel_4.9_%E6%AD%B7%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88&d=jvrVuC1EnGYqPiLc79gNeWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=f54ae074\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkepc.com/14709/大幅度修改程式碼_新增機制加強穩定__Linux_Kernel_4.9_歷來最大更新版</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://file.hkepc.net/2016/12/640x480/14185232521327285886.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffile.hkepc.net%2F2016%2F12%2F640x480%2F14185232521327285886.jpg&h=07293be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLinux 系統日前推出 Linux Kernel 4.9 版本更新，被譽為 Linux 之父的 Linus Torvalds 更指是次版本為 Linux 歷來最大型更新<img src=\"https://ka-sir.xyz/p/HKG_icon/BrainMonster/9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fka-sir.xyz%2Fp%2FHKG_icon%2FBrainMonster%2F9.gif&h=c9480ace&s={SIZE}\" />，其程式碼修改幅度相對過去的更新版更為豐富及優化，將 Linux 推向更為完善的系統。<br />\n<br />\nLinux Kernel 4.9 版本為最新 Linux 系統內核，於 10 月 15 日正式開放公測讓開發者率先試用測試，並於 12 月初推出 Release Candidate (RC) 版本，旋即推出 4.9 正式版，隨後將陸續登錄 Arch Linux 、 Solus 、 openSUSE 、 Tumbleweed 、 Fedora 等 GNU/Linu 系統上<img src=\"https://ka-sir.xyz/p/HKG_icon/BrainMonster/48.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fka-sir.xyz%2Fp%2FHKG_icon%2FBrainMonster%2F48.gif&h=f91da6f0&s={SIZE}\" />。<br />\n<br />\nLinux Kernel 4.9 提供多項重要更新及改善，支援新開發的 Vmapped kernel stacks 機制，利用虛擬映射核心層配置管理記憶體分頁，系統能即時識別個別問題層，預防系統出現嚴重問題前解決<img src=\"https://ka-sir.xyz/p/HKG_icon/BrainMonster/58.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fka-sir.xyz%2Fp%2FHKG_icon%2FBrainMonster%2F58.gif&h=ee66b2b3&s={SIZE}\" />， Linux 核心安全進一步提升<img src=\"https://ka-sir.xyz/p/HKG_icon/BrainMonster/72.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fka-sir.xyz%2Fp%2FHKG_icon%2FBrainMonster%2F72.gif&h=515086fd&s={SIZE}\" />。另外， Linux Kernel 4.9 支援達 29 款 ARM 架構裝置，適用於流動裝置或物聯網裝置，兼容度更強<img src=\"https://ka-sir.xyz/p/HKG_icon/BrainMonster/53.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fka-sir.xyz%2Fp%2FHKG_icon%2FBrainMonster%2F53.gif&h=b30caee5&s={SIZE}\" />。<br />\n<br />\n同時， Linux Kernel 4.9 新增 Memory Protection Key 機制，開發者需採用 pkey 機制控制記億體分頁存取權限，不少編譯器如 GCC 及 LLVM/Clang 已先後作出支援，其後 Intel 處理器亦將支援此機制。同時，受惠於已停止的 Project Ara 模組化手機計劃，當中的 Grebus 硬體協定為 Linux 4.9 帶來豐富相關程式碼，有利於日後運用到 Linux 不同裝置上。<br />\n <br />\nLinux Kernel 4.9 針對 AMD 繪圖核心亦作出多項更新及支援，新增 GCN 1.0 實驗模式，可手動關閉 GNC 1.0 並啟動 GCN 1.1/CIK 版本以進行 AMD 繪圖核心 Direct Rendering Manager 功能，讓舊款 AMD 繪圖卡能使用新版本的驅動程式，得到更高效能的 3D 繪圖加速。<br />\n<br />\nLinux Kernel 4.9 download link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v4.x/linux-4.9.tar.xz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.kernel.org%2Fpub%2Flinux%2Fkernel%2Fv4.x%2Flinux-4.9.tar.xz&d=jvrVuC1EnGYqPiLc79gNeWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=396274f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v4.x/linux-4.9.tar.xz</a>"},{"pid":"2e165ff564adbcd7574d63b44b8b8463e8e93aba","tid":39213,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:23:48.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"8bf90d5d7cab044a6fbe2cf23ccf61ab64fec560","tid":39213,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:28:08.000Z","msg":"in Linus we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf92598ac4e3d93ffcc59a0bb269e39c8f2ae77f","tid":39213,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:35:15.000Z","msg":"happy coding, bros"},{"pid":"d0eb7e7c765b3843fd259a71eb3b642afa911952","tid":39213,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>in Linus we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJust as &quot;In Linux we trust&quot;, &quot;In Joe we f**k&quot; always holds true! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eeb2adcae9773dc99b71d767bd93724a5318a42","tid":39213,"uid":34161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:59:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>in Linus we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJust as &quot;In Linux we trust&quot;, &quot;In Joe we f**k&quot; always holds true! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI like offending people, because I think people who get offended <em>should</em> be offended."},{"pid":"51c3d6b1ea5cb756ad9e51807c9574b177a2505d","tid":39213,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:13:11.000Z","msg":"Project Ara <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249ede7e943dcc41aaa4159df56cfdc57b585205","tid":39213,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Project Ara <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}